Synopsis
Stock Market Today | Diwali Muhurat Trading 2025 Live: For the first time, NSE and BSE are shifting Diwali Muhurat Trading to an afternoon slot from 1:45 pm to 2:45 pm on October 21, marking Samvat 2082. The sacred session blends faith and finance, with rituals like Chopda Pujan preceding trades. Pre-open begins at 1:30 pm, and closing ends by 3:15 pm.
Stock Market Today | Diwali Muhurat Trading 2025 Live: Muhurat Trading 2025| Sensex | Nifty 50 | Stock Market Live Updates: For the first time in decades, NSE and BSE are shifting Diwali Muhurat Trading to an afternoon slot (1:45–2:45 pm) on October 21, marking Samvat 2082.
1 New Update
Largecaps, especially those in banking and technology, continue to offer better visibility amid global uncertainty. Sectors such as banking, IT, and auto witnessed modest gains, with Reliance Industries, ICICI Bank, and TCS also trading higher.
Investors, both retail and institutional, typically place token trades during this session to mark the beginning of a new financial cycle, believing it brings good fortune and prosperity. Market sentiment was further buoyed by strong earnings expectations and easing global uncertainties.
Analysts said investors are entering Samvat 2082 with a cautiously optimistic outlook.
Analysts said investors are entering Samvat 2082 with a cautiously optimistic outlook.
